reviewText: this is a series called DarCrow it was just renamed.  the disc are even labled darg

ASM has repackaged the series DARCROWS with a misleading title TABOO: Charming Sisters. IF they would have included the complete series vs the first 2 episodes it may have been worth the price paid! The bonus features are terrible at best, Don't buy this one.
It said "taboo charming sisters" on the cover but the movie was actually "darcrows".  It wasn't even the complete series of "darcrows".  I don't think this whole transaction deserves one star.
